     F* ------------------------------               *
     F* PARAMETER
     F*  IN   P1SHN1  5    IAF PART1
     F*  "    P1SHN2  5    IAF PART2
     F*  "    P1SHN3  2    IAF PART3
     F*  OUT  P9BZK   40   COMPLETE BZ WEIGH
     F*  "    P9DSK   40   COMPLETE DS WEIGH
     F*  "    P9JCK   40   COMPLETE JC WEIGH
     F*  "    P9BZI   40   IN PROCESS (BZ       )
     F*  "    P9DSI   40   IN PROCESS (DS       )
     F*  "    P9JCI   40   IN PROCESS (JC       )
     F*  "    P9PLBZ  40   PRELOAD (BZ       )
     F*  "    P9PLDS  40   PRELOAD (DS       )
     F*  "    P9PLJC  40   PRELOAD (JC       )
     F*  "    P9LPLD  80   LAST PRELOAD DATE
     F*  "    P9LPLT  60   LAST PRELOAD TIME
JW1  F*  "    P9PLPD  80   PT BF OUT DATE
"    F*  "    P9PLPS  40   PT SHIP PRELOAD
     F************************************************
     FALCPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
      * BZ LOADING
     FAJSPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAJSPL16 IF  E           K        DISK
      * BZ UNLOADING
     FAJSPL2B IF  E           K        DISK
