     C           P1PPR2    WHEQ 'DS'
     C           WMAIS     SUB  P9DSI     P9PLDS
     C                     OTHER
     C           WMAIS     SUB  P9JCI     P9PLJC
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     CSR         ESB100    ENDSR
